    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/3e5b6b2a7091dca0f8201c6fb3ce8819.webp?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the reins as Manager of your very own Borubot team. Catch promising rookies, or sign seasoned veterans on the transfer market, then train, upgrade and maybe even sell them for profit to assemble a first-team squad capable of challenging for top spot. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your hand-picked team in heart-pounding, twin-stick shooter matches, climb the league table, and show you’ve got the tactical nous to climb up through the leagues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/65b814257bfd618397c05b179a6abb6c.webp?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=48 /></span><br>To compete in the league you'll firstly need bots, which can be caught by beating them at &quot;BotJack&quot;:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/b72a32da40ae59d13b5def7f495adb4f.poster.avif?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/b72a32da40ae59d13b5def7f495adb4f.webm?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/b72a32da40ae59d13b5def7f495adb4f.mp4?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/a2d97b8995a5393cf9f6208992f87ceb.webp?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matches consist of intense twin-stick combat, using a variety of bots and weapon choices:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/c872959c02997cb8fac0c7a0863cfdad.poster.avif?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/c872959c02997cb8fac0c7a0863cfdad.webm?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/c872959c02997cb8fac0c7a0863cfdad.mp4?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/75c39a991b8269ef7904b2a5b73e9d70.poster.avif?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/75c39a991b8269ef7904b2a5b73e9d70.webm?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/75c39a991b8269ef7904b2a5b73e9d70.mp4?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/8a41dddb79fa33e04b122eb5d414ccfc.webp?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an open world day and night between league matches. Discover new bots in distant lands and meet other trainers to challenge:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/667a0752bd2bff0db72ca8c3c874b5ce.poster.avif?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/667a0752bd2bff0db72ca8c3c874b5ce.webm?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/667a0752bd2bff0db72ca8c3c874b5ce.mp4?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/f6d8a4c7fc04c2f4c068abe307abc4cc.webp?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train and upgrade your ever changing team of bots from weak juniors to battle hardened, aging veterans:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/603204748b1976e8eff32cb6fc6737dd.poster.avif?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/603204748b1976e8eff32cb6fc6737dd.webm?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/603204748b1976e8eff32cb6fc6737dd.mp4?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/42eff4b6658a8e62827a7949d3e1b7c6.poster.avif?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/42eff4b6658a8e62827a7949d3e1b7c6.webm?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/42eff4b6658a8e62827a7949d3e1b7c6.mp4?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/5e4c8d878527d0325ea73399f2a9f9da.webp?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win or lose matches to gain fans and rise (or fall) through the leagues:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/1fac2750dc26bc14fca79784b9d74c63.poster.avif?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/1fac2750dc26bc14fca79784b9d74c63.webm?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/1fac2750dc26bc14fca79784b9d74c63.mp4?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/8da32bfa371ed6e1eafe69eb332bc7cd.poster.avif?t=1747733290\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/8da32bfa371ed6e1eafe69eb332bc7cd.webm?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140920/extras/8da32bfa371ed6e1eafe69eb332bc7cd.mp4?t=1747733290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p 